---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Mad Learning Lab — Research, evaluation, and capacity-building consulting">
  <section class="hero">
    <span class="eyebrow">Mad Learning Lab</span>
    <h1 class="hero-headline">We bridge the research-to-practice gap, turning insights into <em>feasible action</em>.</h1>
    <p class="hero-body">
      At Mad Learning Lab, we create custom research, evaluation, planning, and skill-building
      solutions that fit your organization's specific needs and challenges. We work in two ways:
      providing high-quality evaluation services and building lasting skills in your team. This helps
      organizations that have complex measurement needs but limited resources. Our approach not only
      gives you the evaluation services you need right now but also teaches your program managers
      practical skills to measure your long-term impact.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta">
      Get in touch
      <span class="cta-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    </a>
  </section>
</Base>
